              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37170459/" class="">第44页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/auntbear/" class=" " title="熊阿姨">熊阿姨</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37170459">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37170459/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p37170459-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">P44.
    是因为在岁月的侵蚀下，她的羽翼与活力损耗殆尽罢了。她在世上的日子，没生过一天病。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-02-12 23:52</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                P44.
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p37170459-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p37170459-2.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p37170459-3.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p37170459-4.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>是因为在岁月的侵蚀下，她的羽翼与活力损耗殆尽罢了。她在世上的日子，没生过一天病。
